2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, ritmeester
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the person drinking juice is the person eating mango##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
